British
airways
Concorde
Complete Concorde
Flight Schedule
This schedule includes convenient connecting U. S. flights to and
from Washington, D. C. for departure or arrival on Concorde. It
also lists connecting flights between London and other cities on
the European continent.
Please remember that all flight schedules are subject to change and
should be confirmed as your final plans are made.
The Concorde
Daylight Flights
BA 578
Concorde departs Washington, D. C. each Sunday and Friday at
1245 p.m. and arrives in London at 2135 p.m.
BA 579
Concorde leaves London each Thursday and Saturday at 1300 p.m.
and arrives in Washington, D. C. at 1150 a.m.
